snippet.title: SCP - Nine Tailed Fox Mod v0.2.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for the upcoming 0.2.0 version now to commemorate the 8 year anniversary of SCP:CB's first release!
Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/ThirdSubdivisionStudios
Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/rEsVY7Y
Join our subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/scpntf
ModDB page of the mod: https://www.moddb.com/mods/scpntf

Additional thanks to Stealthy Zoroark for recording SCP-035, MTF and CI lines!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbW-K1z9HSMhwm3BSwO5WMQ
